---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="China Trip Checklist"
  description="A practical China trip checklist for first-time visitors covering payment apps, internet access, hotel location, addresses, and transport planning."
  canonical="/tools/china-trip-checklist/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <div class="page-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Travel tool</span>
      <h1>China Trip Checklist</h1>
      <p>
        Use this checklist before your first China trip. It focuses on the everyday details that can slow travelers
        down: payment, internet, addresses, hotels, transport, and daily planning.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Pre-trip checklist</h2>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Install Alipay or WeChat Pay and connect a payment card before departure.</li>
          <li>Keep a backup card and a small amount of cash for emergencies.</li>
          <li>Choose an eSIM, roaming plan, or local SIM option for internet access.</li>
          <li>Save your hotel name, address, and nearby landmark in Chinese.</li>
          <li>Book hotels near a metro line or the area where you will spend most of your time.</li>
          <li>Install a map app, translation app, ride-hailing app, and train booking option.</li>
          <li>Group each day by neighborhood to avoid long cross-city travel.</li>
          <li>Save passport scans, hotel bookings, tickets, and emergency contacts offline.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Copyable planning note</h2>
        <div class="copy-box">
          <pre>China trip basics:
- Arrival city:
- Hotel Chinese name and address:
- Nearby metro station:
- Internet plan:
- Payment app tested:
- Day 1 route:
- Backup payment:
- Emergency contact:</pre>
        </div>

        <h2>Related guides</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/china-travel/">First-Time China Travel Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/china-travel-checklist-first-time-visitors/">China Travel Checklist for First-Time Visitors</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/">All tools</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="notice-box">
          <h2>Quick tip</h2>
          <p>Save Chinese addresses before you land. It makes taxis, ride-hailing, and hotel check-in much easier.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
